description: Tasked with picking someone up from the airport? Just get their flight number and you can ask Landing Times for updated arrival information throughout the day. Supported airlines include Air Canada, Alaska, American, Delta, Frontier, Hawaiian, Porter, Southwest, Spirit, United, and Virgin America. Information source: FlightAware.com
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Landing Times when American flight three forty lands
Alexa, ask Landing Times what time United flight seven ninety nine lands in Dallas
Alexa, ask Landing Times for supported airlines
